這是[[美國職棒|美國職棒]]中的生涯打擊率排行榜，規定打席須超過3000才予以計算。現今打擊王是[[泰·柯布|泰·柯布]]，他在大聯盟打了24個球季，生涯打擊率為3成66。<ref name="list">{{cite web|url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/leaders/batting_avg_career.shtml|title=Career Leaders & Records for Batting Average|work=Baseball-Reference.com|accessdate=May 3, 2018|archive-date=2019-07-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190710162423/https://www.baseball-reference.com/leaders/batting_avg_career.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>[[羅傑·霍斯比|羅傑·霍斯比]]拿下7次國聯打擊王，他在1924年更是以4成24打擊率締造1900年後的國聯單季打擊率紀錄。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/players/h/hornsro01.shtml|title=Rogers Hornsby Statistics and History|accessdate=November 18, 2010|work=Baseball-Reference.com|archive-date=2021-02-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210202084354/https://www.baseball-reference.com/players/h/hornsro01.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>

[[無鞋喬·傑克森|喬·傑克森]]雖然生涯打擊率排在歷史第三，不過他在[[1919年世界大賽|1919年世界大賽]]被認為參與放水而遭到永久禁賽。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://espn.go.com/classic/s/black_sox_moments.html|title=SportsCenter Flashback: The Chicago Black Sox banned from baseball|work=ESPN Classic|publisher=ESPN Internet Ventures|accessdate=January 6, 2013|archive-date=2016-07-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160718205751/http://espn.go.com/classic/s/black_sox_moments.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>排名第四的[[雷夫提·歐杜爾|雷夫提·歐杜爾]]原本是名投手，不過他在手臂受傷後改練野手，並拿下2次打擊王。<ref>McKenna, Brian. [http://sabr.org/bioproj/person/b820a06c "Lefty O'Doul"] {{Wayback|url=http://sabr.org/bioproj/person/b820a06c |date=20200423220552 }}. ''SABR.org''. Retrieved January 2, 2013.</ref>排名第五的[[艾德·迪拉杭提|艾德·迪拉杭提]]原本能將打擊率繼續往上衝高，卻在1903年意外於尼加拉瀑布墜落身亡。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.baseballlibrary.com/ballplayers/player.php?name=ed_delahanty_1867 |title=The Ballplayers – Ed Delahanty |work=BaseballLibrary.com |publisher=The Idea Logical Company, Inc |accessdate=November 18, 2010 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20111215001150/http://www.baseballlibrary.com/ballplayers/player.php?name=ed_delahanty_1867 |archivedate=2011-12-15 |df= }}</ref>

最後一位達成單季4成以上打擊率的[[泰德·威廉斯|泰德·威廉斯]]則是排名第7；<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2002/07/06/sports/ted-williams-red-sox-slugger-and-last-to-hit-.400-dies-at-83.html|title=Ted Williams, Red Sox Slugger And Last to Hit .400, Dies at 83|work=The New York Times Company|accessdate=November 18, 2010|first1=Richard|last1=Goldstein|date=July 6, 2002|archive-date=2019-08-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190831162651/https://www.nytimes.com/2002/07/06/sports/ted-williams-red-sox-slugger-and-last-to-hit-.400-dies-at-83.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>而棒球之神[[貝比·魯斯|貝比·魯斯]]則是排名第10。

